drug.absorption:
Cmax = 2.5 μg/mL;
Tmax = 4 hours; 
AUC = 70.4 μg*h/mL; 
Cmax, steady-state = 3.9 μg/mL;
AUC, steady-state = 58.3 μg*h/mL;
The mean relative bioavailability of tablets compared to an oral solution is 69% to 83%.

